STYLING RULES
────────────────────────────────────────

Use only Tailwind utility classes. No inline styles. No external UI libraries.

Status color mapping (Tailwind classes):
  pending:   bg-amber-50  text-amber-800  border-amber-200
  paid:      bg-blue-50   text-blue-800   border-blue-200
  shipped:   bg-purple-50 text-purple-800 border-purple-200
  delivered: bg-green-50  text-green-800  border-green-200
  cancelled: bg-red-50    text-red-800    border-red-200

All cards: bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl
