  dark:bg-gray-900 for page background
  dark:bg-gray-800 for cards and panels
  dark:border-gray-700 for borders
  dark:text-gray-100 for primary text
  dark:text-gray-400 for muted text

────────────────────────────────────────
IMPORTANT CONSTRAINTS
────────────────────────────────────────

1. The 3 views are views of the same data — NOT separate pages. Do not refetch on view switch.
2. Never mutate status backwards (e.g. delivered → shipped is forbidden in UI and in mutation).
3. Guest orders (client_id = null) must display gracefully — never crash on missing client join.
4. All money values must display with 2 decimal places using toLocaleString or toFixed(2).
5. All dates must use date-fns format(parseISO(date), 'MMM d, yyyy').
6. UUID columns displayed in UI must always be truncated to first 8 chars + "…".
7. The Supabase client must be imported from a single lib/supabase.ts singleton — never instantiated inline.
8. React Query must be configured with retry: 1 and staleTime: 30000 globally.
9. The bulk apply button must be disabled if no status is selected in the dropdown.
10. Cancelled orders must never show a "next status" advance button.